# Coding harness (not voice agents)

Orchestrates Jules / Claude Code: backlog → queued sessions → branch/PR → CI → merge.

## Entry points
- `CodingAgentQueueEngine.tick()` — single orchestration loop (also WorkManager ~2 min)
- Voice: `CREATE_FEATURE`, `REPLAY_FEATURE`, `MERGE_PR`
- UI: Harness button → `HarnessRoute` (QueueDashboard, Projects, Features, …)

## Defaults (Jules)
- `parallelLimit`: 3 · `dailyLimitPerAccount`: 15 · `autoMergeOnCiSuccess`: true

## Key paths
- `shared/.../queue/CodingAgentQueueEngine.kt`
- `shared/.../api/codingagent/` — backend adapters
- `androidApp/.../SettingsManager.kt` — `AgentAccount`, queue policies

## Docs
- `docs/HARNESS.md` · env keys: `docs/ENV_VARS.md` (`JULES_KEY`, `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`, `GITHUB_TOKEN`)
